ygData.messageBody:
Hi low level bard (6) looking for a group to
travel from Keleithin (sp?) through the butcherblock
mountains to deliver a message in Freeport. I can sing us
fast across distance using a song that I have just
scribed. I have accidently found myself in Butcherblock,
and there are some low level monsters, but I have not
made it to the Dwarven City which has access to the
water. Also, I was hoping to do some fishing!!! Let me
know, I may stay for a while, level up and get some
crushbone belts before I travel. Also, I owe these orcs a
few casualties so I will be around. /tell Daevyd if I
am on if you are interested. Thanks all.
